                        <summary>
                            
                            <p>On a slab set up in the western street.</p>						
                            
                            <p>[1481 A.D.]</p>						
                            
                            <p>This inscription is dated Plava, Mārgaḻi 23. It records a sale of land by the <hi rend="italic">Śrībhaṇḍārattār</hi> of Tiruvēṅgaḍamuḍaiyāṉ to Śa . . karāja Śi[ṟu] Tirumalairāja.</p>						
                            
                            <p>Published in Tirupati Devasthanam Inscriptions, Volume IV. No. 168.<note n="115-2">There are eleven more lines in continuation, for which there is no impression in the office.</note></p>						
                            
                        </summary>
                    </msContents>
